WEBVTT

00:04:28.499 --> 00:04:33.219
But because of their dependence on 
sometimes just one pollinator species,

00:04:33.219 --> 00:04:35.099
orchids are also vulnerable,

00:04:35.099 --> 00:04:37.759
and many quickly go extinct.

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:39.009
Over time, though,

00:04:39.009 --> 00:04:42.379
more orchid species have formed 
than died out,

00:04:42.379 --> 00:04:46.519
and orchids are some of the most diverse 
flowering plants.

00:04:46.519 --> 00:04:50.047
